<p>
<a name="obligation">@Vru{{}}@HI{{@EM{{wakenihaikanai}}}}</a> is used by the speaker to indicate that something cannot be done because of some external circumstance.

<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{mada@FG{{@KJ{{determine^post}}:teishoku}}monaindakara,@KJ{{tie^marriage}}suru@EM{{wakenihaikanai}}ndesuyo.}}
